data.description: Spacious and well built home on a huge park-like tract of land 5 minutes from Barker's Corner. Welcome to your new homestead! This home offers privacy and seclusion while being an easy 15 Minute drive to Downtown Covington. Flood zone X/Never flooded offering peace of mind for years to come. Large office can easily be used as fifth bedroom. Detached workshop for convenient storage and room for future projects. Detached shed with garden. Priced per recent appraisal! Schedule your showing today!
